original_title: 美少女戦士セーラームーンＳ うさぎ・愛の戦士への道
overview: The 4th Sailor Moon musical (and the 2nd to get a physical release.) While Usagi Tsukino and her friends are enjoying their summer vacation and planning on making their dreams for the future come true, they must deal with the Death Busters and two new Sailor Senshi who are on the hunt for the Talismans, as well as the arrival of Chibiusa.
title: Sailor Moon S - Usagi - The Path to Become the Warrior of Love
